<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="1000maex">1000maex</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Wikipedia:Neutral_point_of_view/Noticeboard&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4" title="Edit section: 1000maex">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
<p><span class="plainlinks userlinks"><a href="/w/index.php?title=User:1000maex&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="User:1000maex (page does not exist)">1000maex</a> <span class="plainlinks">(<a href="/wiki/User_talk:1000maex" title="User talk:1000maex">talk</a>&#160;<b>·</b> <a href="/wiki/Special:Contributions/1000maex" title="Special:Contributions/1000maex">contribs</a><span class="sysop-show">&#160;<b>·</b> <a href="/wiki/Special:DeletedContributions/1000maex" title="Special:DeletedContributions/1000maex">deleted contribs</a></span>&#160;<b>·</b> <a class="external text" href="//en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Special:Log&amp;user=1000maex">logs</a>&#160;<b>·</b> <a class="external text" href="//en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Special:AbuseLog&amp;wpSearchUser=1000maex">edit filter log</a><span class="sysop-show">&#160;<b>·</b> <a href="/wiki/Special:Block/1000maex" title="Special:Block/1000maex">block user</a></span>&#160;<b>·</b> <a class="external text" href="//en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Special:Log&amp;type=block&amp;page=User:1000maex">block log</a>)</span></span></p>
